- "Auf deiner Reise" / "on your journey" → just say what is actually happening
- "Game-changer" → say what actually changed
- "Mindset shift" → describe the actual realisation
- "Transformativ" / "transformative" → say what actually happened
- "Authentisch" / "authentic" → show it, do not label it
